window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>2015 Audie Award Finalist for Non-Fiction</b></p> <p>From the number-one <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author of <i>Liar's Poker</i> and \"one of the country's most popular business journalists\" (<i>The New York Times</i>) Michael Lewis, comes an engaging new book about Wall Street.&nbsp;</p> <p>Michael Lewis, the best-selling author of <i>Boomerang, The Big Short, The Blind Side, Moneyball</i>, and many others, returns to the financial world to give listeners a ringside seat as the biggest news story in years prepares to hit Wall Street.</p>"; 
